    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)"><date>Friday, 11th of Sivan (May). 1859</date>.</p>
            <p>My dear friend:</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Herewith I am sending to you my speech at <persName>Henry
                    Moses'</persName><lb/> funeral, with the request to translate it at once and to
                have it printed.</p>
            <p><hi rend="underline">This time</hi> you must please me. I am counting on you.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Bravo for having openly expressed your opinion about<lb/>
                <persName>Jellinek</persName>. He himself <sic>wassnut</sic> out on
                    <date>Passover</date> a year ago. But he must,<lb/> he must.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)"><persName>Steinschneider</persName> shouts excitedly against
                    <persName>Benjamin the II</persName>.<lb/> He calls him an ignorant man. Only
                free-masonry supports him.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">The filthiest that have ever appeared are the two eleven<lb/> .....
                of the Judenzeitung, 11, 17 and 18. The attack on <persName>Frankel</persName> and against<lb/>
                <persName>Ullman</persName> in <placeName>Paris</placeName> is a terrible thing.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Again, I repeat that it is a blameworthy thing to print<lb/> such
                things as that of <persName>Berend</persName>; it is contrary to all law and
                justice. It<lb/> is not even old women's talk.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Please send me ten copies of the tenth, eleventh, and 20<lb/> of the
                last one.....</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Finally, I send you hearty greetings.</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">Jonah Bondi</persName>
            </p>
            <p>(For <persName>Jellinek</persName>, <persName>Benjamin II</persName> and
                    <persName>Steinchneider</persName>, see Jewish Encyclopedia.)</p>
        </body>
